[C]As if it's my last mile
[G7]If heartache is the [F]fashion
[C]Then I guess [G7]that I'm in [C]style
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 7}
My lips will miss the tender kiss
[G7]That someone else will [C]know
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 8}
